# SEO Optimizer

## Overview

SEO Optimizer is a free online tool that analyzes your webpage and provides useful SEO recommendations to improve search engine visibility.

## Features

- SEO Score
- Meta Title Analysis
- Meta Description Analysis
- Heading Structure
- Image Alt Check
- Performance Suggestions

## How to Use

1. Enter your website URL.
2. Click "Analyze".
3. Review the SEO report.
4. Apply the suggested improvements.

## Who Can Use It

- Bloggers
- SEO Experts
- Digital Marketers
- Website Owners

